content.rendered:
Directed by Aasmaan Bhardwaj

Written by Aasmaan Bhardwaj, Vishal Bhardwaj

Cast Tabu. Radhika Madan (Lovely). Naseeruddin Shah. Arjun Kapoor(Gopal). Kumud Mishra. Konkona Sen Sharma (Laksmi). Shardul Bharadwaj. Lavishka Gupta (Arjun Kapoor’s Daughter). Vijayant Kohli (Maamu). Rayhan Kadar (Hero). Backagaindancer (Shiddart). Ibne Sadik. Jay Upadhyay (Surti). Umar Sharif (Javed Mufti)

Language Hindi

Producers Rekha Bhardwaj, Vishal Bhardwaj. Ankur Garg, Vikas Mehta, Ashwani Mishra, Luv Ranjan.

Production Luv Films, Production Scope, T-Series Films
